blocks.en:
flowchart TD
  A[CM needs to allocate spectrum] --> B{Non-overlapping channel available?}
  B -- Yes --> C[Assign separate channel]
  B -- No --> D{Can group similar networks in frequency?}
  D -- Yes --> E[Group in frequency domain]
  D -- No --> F[Split channel: time / code / frequency]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
  A[CM 需要分配频谱] --> B{有互不重叠的信道吗?}
  B -- 有 --> C[分配独立信道]
  B -- 没有 --> D{能在频域上将相似网络归组吗?}
  D -- 能 --> E[在频域上归组]
  D -- 不能 --> F[拆分信道: 时域 / 码域 / 频域]
